    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315800/extras/c1516a8f465637982567e8a5ed89818a.avif?t=1764215204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315800/extras_big/c1516a8f465637982567e8a5ed89818a.avif?t=1764215204 width=800 height=458 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315800/extras/ab036d005fe312388fe2929e4e3dbe51.avif?t=1764215204\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公（你）有一个女朋友。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >她是一个清秀、成绩优异、体贴周到的非常温柔的女孩。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >两人过着幸福的日子，但在回家的路上，主人公发生了意外。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当主人公在医院醒来时，发现自己已经忘记了家人、朋友以及女朋友的事情。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了恢复记忆，主人公（你）努力尝试，但也正因为失忆，一些女生借机接近，编造各种谎言。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >主人公是否能够恢复记忆，重新回到和女朋友幸福的日子里呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315800/extras/cd37dbd8e6432bcdd518e1ebb3085ae7.avif?t=1764215204\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315800/extras/f3a54f2b5d623e5f43a3c499ddb37e4d.avif?t=1764215204\" width=616 height=275 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315800/extras/a5ea911a1aff72ad9e392651dade17b0.avif?t=1764215204\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315800/extras/208714b797289a1ac746b8c7e9c8acf6.avif?t=1764215204\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3315800/extras/b90d21f8df4eaf58c25804353ab22c66.avif?t=1764215204\" width=616 height=73 /></span>《蜜糖陷阱：失忆》是一款以男性玩家为主打、拥有流畅live2D动态效果的特色游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >虽然有一个女朋友，却无法抵抗诱惑而出轨。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >借着失忆的借口，尝试建立新的关系。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这是一款充满违背道德规范的游戏！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >其中还包含一些小众的特殊场景！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
